data.text:
2023: Played in three matches in her freshman campaign… Finished with 29 total minutes with 23 coming against St. Francis (Aug. 20).

High School: Played club ball with the Lou Fusz Girls Academy ... Won the State Cup Championship in 2019 ... Named team captain for three years ... Earned a spot on the Midwest Regional League Best XI in 2019 ... Selected to the Elite 8 in the Girls Academy League National Playoff in 2022 ... Was a three-year starter for Eureka ... Named an all-conference honoree in 2022 ... Collected a 4.0 GPA ... Was a member of the National Honor Society, ECrew Student Leadership, and newspaper staff at Eureka.

Personal: Daughter of Brian and Christy Dunham ... Has one sister, Libby and one brother, Cooper ... Majoring in Communication Sciences and Disorders.
